\cf0 Other complications include that TiVo provides SkipMode only on top 20 channels, only on certain types of shows (not live news or sports), and even then only on certain shows. Furthermore, SkipMode data arrives later than the show (anywheres from a few minutes to about four hours) and sometimes not at all. You can change which channels might have SkipMode in Preferences>Channels Finally, SkipMode is not available on TiVo's Suggestions, at least until you save the show for later viewing.\
We've worked very hard to make this as easy as possible to take advantage of SkipMode, while falling back to comskip as needed.  By default, SkipMode is off, as it can interfere with your viewing. So, your easiest path to use SkipMode is:\
