\ls1\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	1.	}Enable "Prefer SkipMode to comskip" in Preferences>General.\
{\listtext	2.	}Enable "Auto SkipMode Active from" and give it a range of time each day that you're NOT going to be watching TV.\
{\listtext	3.	}Choose whether to Cut or Mark Commercials.\
{\listtext	4.	}For each subscription and existing download, enable SkipMode column.\
